<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">为进一步扩大反诈宣传覆盖面，提高广大群众防骗意识，国家反诈中心制作了《防范电信网络诈骗宣传手册》，向广大人民群众介绍了十种常见的电信网络诈骗类型，揭批了诈骗犯罪手法、文末有防骗神器，同时进行了防骗提示。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468180011095854.jpg" title="1723468180011095854.jpg" alt="71b60d5bd530d5472877e3506f0ca582.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468225133080570.jpg" title="1723468225133080570.jpg" alt="7b1b02e2e4be104a0aed179558a801ea.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468245794000820.jpg" title="1723468245794000820.jpg" alt="9586bed8c2b10469c64d73fbba6d9432.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468264913057370.jpg" title="1723468264913057370.jpg" alt="4d0b63d00bce5b1e0aa36d4830709d4e.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468286702023391.jpg" title="1723468286702023391.jpg" alt="c9c196854decd0831aaacd4f5acf10c0.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468305362046089.jpg" title="1723468305362046089.jpg" alt="d1f98f66bf40db7865fdd370dcfba70d.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468326908096023.jpg" title="1723468326908096023.jpg" alt="6f63c85ecd97f4ef883b11219f82156a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468341962085553.jpg" title="1723468341962085553.jpg" alt="43cb51b29a34cbc08026cd1d0f5b6dd5.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468354363038084.jpg" title="1723468354363038084.jpg" alt="5d1484429d48723de3ffaf7882a3e809.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468367271027250.jpg" title="1723468367271027250.jpg" alt="5a7c42720f76d92cfea8bb2bf0f411c3.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468381346011928.jpg" title="1723468381346011928.jpg" alt="ee5957173a93259e06ebcf18f8e8109d.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468408297006134.jpg" title="1723468408297006134.jpg" alt="404462cb38425e6be3d263ad4b535f4a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468424282049947.jpg" title="1723468424282049947.jpg" alt="b09c421aee6fffec73ad82a4eee50006.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468441722091496.jpg" title="1723468441722091496.jpg" alt="045810facc767504fd5fdb05e33a3b4b.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468452502073851.jpg" title="1723468452502073851.jpg" alt="d3e47c0acaaa9760f7e200a836915366.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468464287012849.jpg" title="1723468464287012849.jpg" alt="ddbb521e16f3f951f7452839dc03f42c.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468475738091205.jpg" title="1723468475738091205.jpg" alt="6cf872b36503025ffa9e1e337da923e5.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468489345014854.jpg" title="1723468489345014854.jpg" alt="0aa623c094e41a6b98d6158aa8391040.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468503336033637.jpg" title="1723468503336033637.jpg" alt="e4e3abc3d5c788013326100f6f0e48a6.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468514711019991.jpg" title="1723468514711019991.jpg" alt="771005590cd97c1b0cf822b5b4a25515.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468530924096164.jpg" title="1723468530924096164.jpg" alt="7184814146d5e789902eb89498e30c2a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468841081068061.jpg" title="1723468841081068061.jpg" alt="c73f40a707607b699cd5d32230578e0a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468855607047711.jpg" title="1723468855607047711.jpg" alt="b884482aac80ae84953fa70eb1f2f6d2.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">电信网络诈骗手法千变万化，但万变不离其宗，记住“三不一多”原则：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">未知链接不点击</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">陌生来电不轻信</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">个人信息不透露</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">转账汇款多核实</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">宣传千万次，从不认真看。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">骗后急报警，天天催破案。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">骗子在境外，警察侦办难。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">破案要条件，防范是关键。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">源头被阻断，哪里有发案？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">信息多转发，人人来宣传。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">伎俩多知晓，防患于未然！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468943974057511.jpg" title="1723468943974057511.jpg" alt="7db498bcfbed5ed240ca437bc26ad187.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468959357009183.jpg" title="1723468959357009183.jpg" alt="344b956821b3980b1d857852af39ca77.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723468978099035191.jpg" title="1723468978099035191.jpg" alt="ac4de85ae9aae9cd96a90b4cb843e27c.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469126889037336.jpg" title="1723469126889037336.jpg" alt="7530249c7fafe5bdbcbba4dbc96cb1a2.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469142778068347.jpg" title="1723469142778068347.jpg" alt="579d0e47e385c79b5d1ccbda9e7693d8.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469157296010209.jpg" title="1723469157296010209.jpg" alt="364fda096131f27c7b2cf929be81aef5.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469239299085480.jpg" title="1723469239299085480.jpg" alt="eabbf17f79bf60640d0daff656236056.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469256685083037.jpg" title="1723469256685083037.jpg" alt="db31de7bcc9be82351bf1ea54913e7eb.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469272056091176.jpg" title="1723469272056091176.jpg" alt="6ca5178a11e1e44a2189216ee08d2a3b.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469308746072320.jpg" title="1723469308746072320.jpg" alt="3cc1154a56ac6f0a5d1150593e20b0f7.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469324005044066.jpg" title="1723469324005044066.jpg" alt="822bf32eb307f4e2bbcb620bc5ea8b5b.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469338641030130.jpg" title="1723469338641030130.jpg" alt="c9a6343a9dbf42a2977d6c37e9cda912.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469655165036813.jpg" title="1723469655165036813.jpg" alt="a25cfcee6061882f1b388f5545816b24.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469669214090739.jpg" title="1723469669214090739.jpg" alt="55423e09fb78668309630284655b7bed.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469686682032336.jpg" title="1723469686682032336.jpg" alt="07b4c3da3dc749057fade629dc383b8a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469702175007328.jpg" title="1723469702175007328.jpg" alt="939586dd4ef43b0e88a1f9ef6958d2b7.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723469715564091436.jpg" title="1723469715564091436.jpg" alt="53ebaf13f8159c06786b3030f805fe10.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723470011446047764.jpg" title="1723470011446047764.jpg" alt="69a6ad9225029a749b0bfb8f41216549.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723470026043073590.jpg" title="1723470026043073590.jpg" alt="231898ef95e643f60731debd32756422.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723470128118085366.jpg" title="1723470128118085366.jpg" alt="c7e5e9fd9653d6583cd1281712e63fbb.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723470170254004858.jpg" title="1723470170254004858.jpg" alt="339a70cdcb13996796446003044a1f48.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240812/1723470190268003073.jpg" title="1723470190268003073.jpg" alt="75f23820e3a436e081fe24c1c296faab.jpg"/></p><p style="t